quoteText: SECTION 12.2 of These terms requires the use of arbitration on an individual basis to resolve disputes ARISING OUT OF THESE TERMS, rather than jury trials or class action LAWSUITS, and also limitS the remedies available to you in the event of a dispute.
title: This service forces users into binding arbitration in the case of disputes
